            <lg xml:id="TK1065">
<l>teṇṇī raṭupuṟkai yāyiṉun tāṭanta </l>
<l>tuṇṇali ṉūṅkiṉiya til</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Even thin gruel is ambrosia to him who has obtained it by labour.</l>
